skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: christmas cheer
des:
Hey kids! Christmas Cheer is a fun skill that gives you a Christmas joke, or "cheer", of the day. This skill is perfect for getting you ready for the holidays. Want a good laugh? Simply say, "tell me a cheer", to start. 

Christmas Cheer is most suitable for children ages 13 and younger.

Ho Ho Ho. Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays, everyone!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
